## Step 3: Code Path Coverage
> **[MEDIUM+]** Goal: 不漏测试 | Inputs: 实现代码diff
<!-- Action: ASCII树追踪每个函数/分支/错误路径的测试覆盖。★★★=边界+错误 ★★=happy ★=冒烟 -->

```
CODE PATH COVERAGE
===========================
[+] path/to/module.ts
    ├── fn()
    │   ├── [★★★ TESTED] desc — file:line
    │   └── [GAP]         desc — NO TEST

USER FLOW COVERAGE
===========================
[+] Feature flow
    ├── [★★★ TESTED] desc — file:line
    └── [GAP] [→E2E] desc — NO TEST

─────────────────────────────────
COVERAGE: N/M (X%) | QUALITY: ★★★:N ★★:N ★:N
GAPS: N (N need E2E, N eval)
```

